00:05:20.970 --> 00:05:21.900
You're right.

00:05:24.690 --> 00:05:26.210
Let's carry those forty dan together.

00:05:33.310 --> 00:05:34.490
Come on, let's go.

00:05:34.950 --> 00:05:36.240
Hurry, move along.

