00:15:03.720 --> 00:15:04.560
Wait.

00:15:04.960 --> 00:15:05.910
Is it true that

00:15:06.600 --> 00:15:07.790
every male of Heaven Rank

00:15:08.040 --> 00:15:09.470
is paired with a lady of Earth Rank?

00:15:26.140 --> 00:15:28.540
♪Watch the storm;
hear the night rain fall♪

00:15:28.540 --> 00:15:30.140
♪Till the light of dawn♪

00:15:30.140 --> 00:15:31.860
♪A truth that cannot be spoken♪

00:15:32.540 --> 00:15:34.220
♪Right and wrong matter♪

00:15:34.220 --> 00:15:36.340
♪Yet I can't make the right choice♪

00:15:36.540 --> 00:15:37.980
♪The lost player in the game♪

00:15:38.220 --> 00:15:41.340
♪Made a move by a twist of fate♪

00:15:41.340 --> 00:15:43.860
♪The way back is lost,
leaving nowhere to return♪

00:15:43.860 --> 00:15:47.100
♪Borrow the endless cycles♪

00:15:47.660 --> 00:15:51.140
♪To fight for the most perfect outcome♪

00:15:51.900 --> 00:15:54.260
♪How to trace the threads
and follow cause and effect♪

00:15:54.260 --> 00:15:58.020
♪Seeking a strategy without flaw♪

00:15:58.300 --> 00:16:02.940
♪How to break free
from this fated yet unforeseen lock♪

00:16:03.100 --> 00:16:08.140
♪To live so as to shake the world♪

00:16:08.500 --> 00:16:12.620
♪With this journey,
I gain a fiercer edge♪

00:16:12.740 --> 00:16:14.820
♪I've planned
before I act countless times♪

00:16:14.900 --> 00:16:21.260
♪Fatal danger turned into a jest♪

00:16:21.380 --> 00:16:25.580
♪Through this road,
I watch the endless rise and fall♪

00:16:25.620 --> 00:16:27.700
♪In the chapters lie ages
of decay and bloom♪

00:16:27.700 --> 00:16:29.620
♪Let us meet again♪

00:16:29.660 --> 00:16:34.820
♪One hurried path, and one at ease♪